{"id":294101,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-各地维权访民抗议园博会在京召开，邓志/","date":"2013-05-18T16:15:40Z","modified":"2013-05-18T16:15:40Z","title":"维权网 | 各地维权访民抗议园博会在京召开，邓志波等人失踪（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>是世界园林博览会召开的第一天，来自全国各地的维权访民也都前来观看世博会。他们是天津郑建慧、吉林邓志波、赵云侠、河北王心灵、鲍润蒲、河南姜小才等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>虽然园博会的六个场馆有着不同的风格，但访民却不许入内出了地铁站门口，通往各个场馆的路全部戒严。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多辆大轿车把访民分别带到久敬庄黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权访民赵云侠巧妙的躲开抓捕，在不同的地点三次撒传单抗议。她儿子见义勇为于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>牺牲。案件已经四年了，第二次发回重审也一年五个月了，法院就一直不开庭审理。赵云侠为此抗议公检法腐败。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>河北鲍润蒲、王心灵、段淑兰、天津郑建慧、吉林陈凤杰、赵云侠、邓志波等更多维权访民隐蔽在不同的地方，随时准备举牌儿抗议，牌子上的内容是：“贺冤博会隆重召开”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>河南访民姜小才、李玉凤、李长河、李晓成、崔喜军、李永红、陈小翠、魏翠玲、等人则举出“河南焦作维权访民贺冤博会召开！让焦作腐败从冤博会走向世界，让世界文明从园博会走进中国”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家一个共同点目标反腐！参加园博会抗议活动的还有：山海的项文寅、江苏邵允黎、黑龙江杜青艳甘肃曹晓龙、曹瑞霞、山西王群凤、辽宁杨秀梅、河北刘敏杰、赵敏等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>点左右，吉林维权人士邓志波和张继新与外界失去联系，陕西维权访民吕动力于下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点在久敬庄被警方带走后也与外界失去联系，另外辽宁维权人士赵广军也与外界失去联系。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人的亲友自下午开始，一直不断拨打他们的手机，赵广军的手机提示为来电转移，其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人的手机都处于关机状态。当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分左右，邓志波的电话畅通，但却处于无人接听状态。至发稿时止，本网信息员仍无法联系上他们之中的任何一人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-PbRYBhhfzo8/UZeeXi81g6I/AAAAAAAAiMw/GjMMqQiP0ZM/s1600/49.09.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-PbRYBhhfzo8/UZeeXi81g6I/AAAAAAAAiMw/GjMMqQiP0ZM/s320/49.09.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tif8Ik3rvGc/UZeebM9QfsI/AAAAAAAAiM4/8Mzy3c6NF18/s1600/2013-05-16+19.22.38.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tif8Ik3rvGc/UZeebM9QfsI/AAAAAAAAiM4/8Mzy3c6NF18/s320/2013-05-16+19.22.38.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hNBiSZkxZng/UZeefGZDKiI/AAAAAAAAiNA/WUWRZZFE3q0/s1600/2013-05-18+10.00.08.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"219\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hNBiSZkxZng/UZeefGZDKiI/AAAAAAAAiNA/WUWRZZFE3q0/s320/2013-05-18+10.00.08.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pC0JAVjHb8g/UZeejT14I7I/AAAAAAAAiNI/VKgLODjDWls/s1600/2013-05-18+10.55.45.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pC0JAVjHb8g/UZeejT14I7I/AAAAAAAAiNI/VKgLODjDWls/s1600/2013-05-18+10.55.45.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-_RSTHJMafzQ/UZeenhCNLuI/AAAAAAAAiNQ/o6J0JWQmHzI/s1600/2013-05-18+11.31.48.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-_RSTHJMafzQ/UZeenhCNLuI/AAAAAAAAiNQ/o6J0JWQmHzI/s320/2013-05-18+11.31.48.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DwlQRQk0IOw/UZeetsDpkoI/AAAAAAAAiNY/tuSE3ESVrIk/s1600/DSCN3160.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DwlQRQk0IOw/UZeetsDpkoI/AAAAAAAAiNY/tuSE3ESVrIk/s320/DSCN3160.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>